summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from John H. McGraw, as Executor of the Estate of May L. McGraw, to the City of Seattle, dated the 31st day of August, 1908, to a portion of Lot three (3) Section Twenty-one (21) Township Twenty-five (25) North of Range Four (4) East W. M. in the Plat of Union City to the City of Seattle.
